    "title": "Kumwamini Mungu katika Isaya",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kumwamini mungu katika isaya",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Nabii Isaya alitambua kwamba wanadamu wanaweza kuwa wasioaminika (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:22\">Isaya 2:22</a>). Wakati wa shida, watu wa Yuda mara nyingi waliomba msaada kutoka kwa mataifa mengine kama Misri au Ashuru. Hata hivyo, Isaya alieleza kwamba mafanikio na usalama wa Yuda vilitegemea kumtumaini Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:9-Isa8:17\">Isaya 8:9–17</a>). Jeshi la Ashuru lilimdhihaki Mfalme Hezekia kwa kumtumaini Mungu, lakini imani hii ilisababisha ushindi mkubwa kwa watu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:1-Isa37:37\">Isaya 36:1–37:37</a>).</p><p>Wale wanaomwamini Bwana wanahisi heshima kubwa kwake na hawaogopi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:23\">29:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:4\">35:4</a>). Hii ni kwa sababu wanajua Bwana yuko pamoja nao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12\">51:12</a>). Wanamsifu kwa sababu wanamwamini (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:2\">12:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:9\">25:9</a>). Wanaonyesha imani yao kwa kumtii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:8\">26:8</a>).</p><p>Watu waminifu wa Mungu wanaweza kuona athari za hukumu yake juu ya maadui zake wanapongojea wokovu wa Bwana. Hata hivyo, wanapata nguvu mpya kila siku (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:31\">40:31</a>). Wanajiona kama raia wa mji wa Mungu, Sayuni (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:1-Isa26:3\">26:1–3</a>). Wale wanaomwamini Bwana wana amani ya kweli na ya kudumu ndani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">26:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17-Isa32:18\">32:17–18</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:22\">Isaya 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:4-Isa7:9\">7:4–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:16-Isa8:20\">8:16–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:2\">12:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:2-Isa26:3\">26:2–3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17-Isa32:18\">32:17–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:4\">35:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9-Isa40:11\">40:9–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28-Isa40:31\">28–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12\">51:12</a></p>",
